column2: SELECT TOP #  p.objid,p.ra,p.dec,p.u,p.g,p.r,p.i,p.z,  p.spaceobjid, s.class,s.z as redshift, p.petroR5#_r,  SM.logMass FROM PhotoObj AS p  JOIN SpecObj AS s ON s.bestobjid = p.objid  JOIN dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq(#, #,#) AS N ON p.objid =N.objID  JOIN stellarMassFSPSGranEarlyNoDust AS SM ON s.spaceObjID = SM.spaceObjID WHERE   s.Z BETWEEN # AND #
